Some People daydream about what they can become in this life, others wonder what they were in past lives! Bryn Blankinship is a 2nd generation hypnotherapist, instructor, & author who joins Beyond the Darkness to talk about different past life, afterlife, and alien life experiences and exploring the many aspects of a soul's existence!
